110
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,790
- Bamee!
- Bamee!

111
00:06:17,370 --> 00:06:19,660
- Bamee!
- He's still alive.

112
00:06:20,080 --> 00:06:21,350
Oh!

113
00:06:22,070 --> 00:06:23,859
