to get back home.

158
00:08:52,964 --> 00:08:54,624
That's a good idea.

159
00:09:20,650 --> 00:09:22,010
I'm here.

160
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,630
You don't have to be scared.

161
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:12,000
I will call mommy for help.

162
00:10:14,250 --> 00:10:15,670
Don't be dramatic!

163
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:19,180
I was just hugging you to
comfort you after Bamee's accident.

164
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,270
You're the most caring person.

165
00:10:26,130 --> 00:10:27,810
So cute!

166
00:10:44,710 --> 00:10:46,810
Let's sleep now.

167
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,560
Who are you?

168
00:11:43,640 --> 00:11:45,219
