177
00:12:14,310 --> 00:12:15,800
Bamee!

178
00:12:16,460 --> 00:12:18,679
Here, finish them all.

179
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:20,150
You'll get well soon.

180
00:12:20,900 --> 00:12:22,150
Thank you, Baiwan.

181
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:24,000
How are you?

182
00:12:24,310 --> 00:12:25,900
