Share some with Kiew.

187
00:12:37,424 --> 00:12:38,514
Who is Kiew?

188
00:12:38,740 --> 00:12:39,660
Oh,

189
00:12:40,270 --> 00:12:41,190
Oh,

190
00:12:41,543 --> 00:12:43,233
