of not remembering Kiew?

191
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,380
This is not a trick.

192
00:12:46,110 --> 00:12:47,170
I mean it.

193
00:12:52,640 --> 00:12:53,770
Bamee.

194
00:12:56,756 --> 00:12:59,165
Bamee, how are you?

195
00:12:59,190 --> 00:13:00,340
Mommy!

196
00:13:06,540 --> 00:13:10,110
You are the first one I think of
when I woke up.

197
00:13:20,020 --> 00:13:21,919
I really don't know him.

198
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:23,970
I feel irritated when I see him.

199
00:13:25,990 --> 00:13:27,260
Get out of my room.

200
00:13:27,983 --> 00:13:29,813
Don't chase him away like that.

201
00:13:29,960 --> 00:13:31,290
Kiew is your friend.

202
00:13:33,030 --> 00:13:35,750
Bamee, can't you remember
anything about Kiew?

203
00:13:39,710 --> 00:13:40,780
No, I can't.

204
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:52,080
I just heard from aunt Pim,

205
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,610
