218
00:14:38,450 --> 00:14:40,840
Can you be specific?

219
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,370
1 week,

220
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,160
1 month,

221
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:45,650
or 1 year.

222
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:47,880
I can't be specific.

223
00:14:48,700 --> 00:14:50,739
