258
00:16:55,696 --> 00:16:57,805
Bamee has to stay
at the condo with Kiew?

259
00:16:57,830 --> 00:16:59,139
It's the only way, Pim,

260
00:16:59,140 --> 00:17:01,870
for them to experience the same things
they've done together.

261
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:05,739
But right now, Bamee doesn't like Kiew.

262
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:07,250
He won't do it.

263
00:17:07,500 --> 00:17:08,850
But, Pim,

264
00:17:09,010 --> 00:17:10,700
you have to help us.

265
00:17:12,320 --> 00:17:14,960
Right now,
Bamee listens to you the most.

